imately achieved.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aOperax19th century. 0aOperay19th century. 7aMUSIC / Genres & Styles / Opera.2bisacsh  aclassical music.  acontroversial composer.  adeathridge.  ader ring des nibelungen.  aengaging assessment.  afamous classical composers.  amusic appreciation.  amusic history.  aperforming arts.  aprovocative actions.  atristan and isolde.  aunderstanding wagner.  aunpublished musical sketches.  awagner.  awestern art tradition.  awestern music canon.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of California Press Backlist Package 2000-2013z978311069042240uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/978052093461040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520934610423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780520934610/original  a978-3-11-069042-2  University of California Press Backlist Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles